# UI Constraints

- Prioritize mobile-first layouts and touch-friendly controls.
- Preserve dark mode compatibility for new and modified UI elements.
- Keep dense interactions clear and readable on small screens.
- Place heavy interactivity in client components and keep data fetching server-side where practical.
